        transactionReportInstruction TransactionReportInstruction (1..1)
        defaultValue number (1..1)
    output:
        callAmount number (0..1)

    set callAmount:
        cdeV1.quantity.ExtractCallAmount(transactionReportInstruction, defaultValue)

